"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dkr1665702733399.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dkr1665702733399.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dkr1665702733399.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dkr1665702733399\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      u36_compatibility\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Support LONG/LONG RAW data types in the U6.x connector\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dkr1665702733399__topic_d56045e1_d56046e1_d56047e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dkr1665702733399__p_d56048e1_d56049e1_d56050e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ORA_PARAMS = u36_compatibility</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dkr1665702733399__section_wpt_qr4_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d281326e60\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dkr1665702733399__p_d56075e1_d56076e1_d56077e1\">This option applies only to the U6.x connector and\n            above.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dkr1665702733399__section_vbs_rr4_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d281326e69\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dkr1665702733399__p_d56060e1_d56061e1_d56062e1\">Use with the U6.x connector to add support for\n            LONG/LONG RAW data types, as in the U3.6 connector. The U3.6 connector supported\n            LONG/LONG RAW data type, but not the CLOB/BLOB data type.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526860\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526860\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "u36_compatibility Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 u36_compatibility Support LONG/LONG RAW data types in the U6.x connector USYS$ORA_PARAMS = u36_compatibility Use This option applies only to the U6.x connector and above. Description Use with the U6.x connector to add support for LONG/LONG RAW data types, as in the U3.6 connector. The U3.6 connector supported LONG/LONG RAW data type, but not the CLOB/BLOB data type. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}